{
  "book": "1nephi",
  "bookName": "1 Nephi",
  "chapter": 3,
  "voice": {
    "provider": "elevenlabs",
    "voice_id": "ddDFRErfhdc2asyySOG5",
    "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
    "settings": {
      "stability": 0.5,
      "similarity_boost": 0.75,
      "style": 0.35,
      "use_speaker_boost": true
    },
    "name": "Samuel"
  },
  "pauses": {
    "line_ms": 180,
    "verse_ms": 500
  },
  "duration": 386.967,
  "lines": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 3.715,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that I, Nephi, returned from speaking with the Lord,",
      "verse": "3:1",
      "lineIndex": 0
    },
    {
      "start": 3.895,
      "end": 5.52,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to the tent of my father.",
      "verse": "3:1",
      "lineIndex": 1
    },
    {
      "start": 6.2,
      "end": 9.311,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that he spake unto me, saying:",
      "verse": "3:2",
      "lineIndex": 3
    },
    {
      "start": 9.491,
      "end": 11.767,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold I have dreamed a dream,",
      "verse": "3:2",
      "lineIndex": 4
    },
    {
      "start": 11.947,
      "end": 14.362,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in the which the Lord hath commanded me",
      "verse": "3:2",
      "lineIndex": 5
    },
    {
      "start": 14.542,
      "end": 18.071,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that thou and thy brethren shall return to Jerusalem.",
      "verse": "3:2",
      "lineIndex": 6
    },
    {
      "start": 18.751,
      "end": 22.373,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For behold, Laban hath the record of the Jews",
      "verse": "3:3",
      "lineIndex": 7
    },
    {
      "start": 22.553,
      "end": 25.339,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also a genealogy of my forefathers,",
      "verse": "3:3",
      "lineIndex": 8
    },
    {
      "start": 25.519,
      "end": 28.305,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they are engraven upon plates of brass.",
      "verse": "3:3",
      "lineIndex": 9
    },
    {
      "start": 28.985,
      "end": 31.446,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, the Lord hath commanded me",
      "verse": "3:4",
      "lineIndex": 10
    },
    {
      "start": 31.626,
      "end": 35.898,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that thou and thy brothers should go unto the house of Laban,",
      "verse": "3:4",
      "lineIndex": 11
    },
    {
      "start": 36.078,
      "end": 37.564,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and seek the records,",
      "verse": "3:4",
      "lineIndex": 12
    },
    {
      "start": 37.744,
      "end": 40.716,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and bring them down hither into the wilderness.",
      "verse": "3:4",
      "lineIndex": 13
    },
    {
      "start": 41.396,
      "end": 43.811,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now, behold thy brothers murmur,",
      "verse": "3:5",
      "lineIndex": 14
    },
    {
      "start": 43.991,
      "end": 47.52,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "saying it is a hard thing which I have required of them;",
      "verse": "3:5",
      "lineIndex": 15
    },
    {
      "start": 47.7,
      "end": 50.208,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "but behold I have not required it of them,",
      "verse": "3:5",
      "lineIndex": 16
    },
    {
      "start": 50.388,
      "end": 53.035,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "but it is a commandment of the Lord.",
      "verse": "3:5",
      "lineIndex": 17
    },
    {
      "start": 53.715,
      "end": 55.248,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Therefore go, my son,",
      "verse": "3:6",
      "lineIndex": 18
    },
    {
      "start": 55.428,
      "end": 57.611,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and thou shalt be favored of the Lord,",
      "verse": "3:6",
      "lineIndex": 19
    },
    {
      "start": 57.791,
      "end": 59.834,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because thou hast not murmured.",
      "verse": "3:6",
      "lineIndex": 20
    },
    {
      "start": 60.514,
      "end": 63.951,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that I, Nephi, said unto my father:",
      "verse": "3:7",
      "lineIndex": 22
    },
    {
      "start": 64.131,
      "end": 67.382,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I will go and do the things which the Lord hath commanded,",
      "verse": "3:7",
      "lineIndex": 23
    },
    {
      "start": 67.562,
      "end": 72.206,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for I know that the Lord giveth no commandments unto the children of men,",
      "verse": "3:7",
      "lineIndex": 24
    },
    {
      "start": 72.386,
      "end": 74.987,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "save he shall prepare a way for them",
      "verse": "3:7",
      "lineIndex": 25
    },
    {
      "start": 75.167,
      "end": 78.278,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they may accomplish the thing which he commandeth them.",
      "verse": "3:7",
      "lineIndex": 26
    },
    {
      "start": 78.958,
      "end": 82.673,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that when my father had heard these words",
      "verse": "3:8",
      "lineIndex": 27
    },
    {
      "start": 82.853,
      "end": 84.664,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "he was exceedingly glad,",
      "verse": "3:8",
      "lineIndex": 28
    },
    {
      "start": 84.844,
      "end": 87.863,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for he knew that I had been blessed of the Lord.",
      "verse": "3:8",
      "lineIndex": 29
    },
    {
      "start": 88.543,
      "end": 93.419,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I, Nephi, and my brethren took our journey in the wilderness,",
      "verse": "3:9",
      "lineIndex": 30
    },
    {
      "start": 93.599,
      "end": 95.178,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "with our tents,",
      "verse": "3:9",
      "lineIndex": 31
    },
    {
      "start": 95.358,
      "end": 97.448,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to go up to the land of Jerusalem.",
      "verse": "3:9",
      "lineIndex": 32
    },
    {
      "start": 98.128,
      "end": 102.958,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that when we had gone up to the land of Jerusalem,",
      "verse": "3:10",
      "lineIndex": 34
    },
    {
      "start": 103.138,
      "end": 106.249,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I and my brethren did consult one with another.",
      "verse": "3:10",
      "lineIndex": 35
    },
    {
      "start": 106.929,
      "end": 108.183,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And we cast lots\u2014",
      "verse": "3:11",
      "lineIndex": 36
    },
    {
      "start": 108.363,
      "end": 111.382,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "who of us should go in unto the house of Laban.",
      "verse": "3:11",
      "lineIndex": 37
    },
    {
      "start": 111.562,
      "end": 114.72,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that the lot fell upon Laman;",
      "verse": "3:11",
      "lineIndex": 38
    },
    {
      "start": 114.9,
      "end": 118.058,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and Laman went in unto the house of Laban,",
      "verse": "3:11",
      "lineIndex": 39
    },
    {
      "start": 118.238,
      "end": 121.396,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he talked with him as he sat in his house.",
      "verse": "3:11",
      "lineIndex": 40
    },
    {
      "start": 122.076,
      "end": 124.723,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he desired of Laban the records",
      "verse": "3:12",
      "lineIndex": 41
    },
    {
      "start": 124.903,
      "end": 128.618,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which were engraven upon the plates of brass,",
      "verse": "3:12",
      "lineIndex": 42
    },
    {
      "start": 128.798,
      "end": 131.724,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which contained the genealogy of my father.",
      "verse": "3:12",
      "lineIndex": 43
    },
    {
      "start": 132.404,
      "end": 135.515,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And behold, it came to pass that Laban was angry,",
      "verse": "3:13",
      "lineIndex": 44
    },
    {
      "start": 135.695,
      "end": 137.971,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and thrust him out from his presence;",
      "verse": "3:13",
      "lineIndex": 45
    },
    {
      "start": 138.151,
      "end": 141.355,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he would not that he should have the records.",
      "verse": "3:13",
      "lineIndex": 46
    },
    {
      "start": 141.535,
      "end": 143.532,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, he said unto him:",
      "verse": "3:13",
      "lineIndex": 47
    },
    {
      "start": 143.712,
      "end": 146.87,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold thou art a robber, and I will slay thee.",
      "verse": "3:13",
      "lineIndex": 48
    },
    {
      "start": 147.55,
      "end": 149.965,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But Laman fled out of his presence,",
      "verse": "3:14",
      "lineIndex": 49
    },
    {
      "start": 150.145,
      "end": 152.978,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and told the things which Laban had done, unto us.",
      "verse": "3:14",
      "lineIndex": 50
    },
    {
      "start": 153.158,
      "end": 155.898,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And we began to be exceedingly sorrowful,",
      "verse": "3:14",
      "lineIndex": 51
    },
    {
      "start": 156.078,
      "end": 160.954,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and my brethren were about to return unto my father in the wilderness.",
      "verse": "3:14",
      "lineIndex": 52
    },
    {
      "start": 161.634,
      "end": 163.677,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But behold I said unto them that:",
      "verse": "3:15",
      "lineIndex": 54
    },
    {
      "start": 163.857,
      "end": 165.39,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "As the Lord liveth,",
      "verse": "3:15",
      "lineIndex": 55
    },
    {
      "start": 165.57,
      "end": 167.01,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and as we live,",
      "verse": "3:15",
      "lineIndex": 56
    },
    {
      "start": 167.19,
      "end": 170.534,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "we will not go down unto our father in the wilderness",
      "verse": "3:15",
      "lineIndex": 57
    },
    {
      "start": 170.714,
      "end": 174.894,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "until we have accomplished the thing which the Lord hath commanded us.",
      "verse": "3:15",
      "lineIndex": 58
    },
    {
      "start": 175.574,
      "end": 177.71,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, let us be faithful",
      "verse": "3:16",
      "lineIndex": 59
    },
    {
      "start": 177.89,
      "end": 180.073,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in keeping the commandments of the Lord;",
      "verse": "3:16",
      "lineIndex": 60
    },
    {
      "start": 180.253,
      "end": 184.665,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "therefore let us go down to the land of our father's inheritance,",
      "verse": "3:16",
      "lineIndex": 61
    },
    {
      "start": 184.845,
      "end": 187.121,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for behold he left gold and silver,",
      "verse": "3:16",
      "lineIndex": 62
    },
    {
      "start": 187.301,
      "end": 189.066,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and all manner of riches.",
      "verse": "3:16",
      "lineIndex": 63
    },
    {
      "start": 189.246,
      "end": 193.147,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And all this he hath done because of the commandments of the Lord.",
      "verse": "3:16",
      "lineIndex": 64
    },
    {
      "start": 193.827,
      "end": 196.567,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For he knew that Jerusalem must be destroyed,",
      "verse": "3:17",
      "lineIndex": 65
    },
    {
      "start": 196.747,
      "end": 198.976,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of the wickedness of the people.",
      "verse": "3:17",
      "lineIndex": 66
    },
    {
      "start": 199.656,
      "end": 202.721,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For behold, they have rejected the words of the prophets.",
      "verse": "3:18",
      "lineIndex": 67
    },
    {
      "start": 202.901,
      "end": 206.012,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, if my father should dwell in the land",
      "verse": "3:18",
      "lineIndex": 68
    },
    {
      "start": 206.192,
      "end": 209.582,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "after he hath been commanded to flee out of the land,",
      "verse": "3:18",
      "lineIndex": 69
    },
    {
      "start": 209.762,
      "end": 211.991,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "behold, he would also perish.",
      "verse": "3:18",
      "lineIndex": 70
    },
    {
      "start": 212.171,
      "end": 215.793,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, it must needs be that he flee out of the land.",
      "verse": "3:18",
      "lineIndex": 71
    },
    {
      "start": 216.473,
      "end": 221.581,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And behold, it is wisdom in God that we should obtain these records,",
      "verse": "3:19",
      "lineIndex": 72
    },
    {
      "start": 221.761,
      "end": 226.312,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that we may preserve unto our children the language of our fathers;",
      "verse": "3:19",
      "lineIndex": 73
    },
    {
      "start": 226.992,
      "end": 229.964,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And also that we may preserve unto them the words",
      "verse": "3:20",
      "lineIndex": 74
    },
    {
      "start": 230.144,
      "end": 233.534,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which have been spoken by the mouth of all the holy prophets,",
      "verse": "3:20",
      "lineIndex": 75
    },
    {
      "start": 233.714,
      "end": 237.615,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which have been delivered unto them by the Spirit and power of God,",
      "verse": "3:20",
      "lineIndex": 76
    },
    {
      "start": 237.795,
      "end": 239.467,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "since the world began,",
      "verse": "3:20",
      "lineIndex": 77
    },
    {
      "start": 239.647,
      "end": 241.876,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "even down unto this present time.",
      "verse": "3:20",
      "lineIndex": 78
    },
    {
      "start": 242.556,
      "end": 247.061,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that after this manner of language did I persuade my brethren,",
      "verse": "3:21",
      "lineIndex": 79
    },
    {
      "start": 247.241,
      "end": 250.817,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they might be faithful in keeping the commandments of God.",
      "verse": "3:21",
      "lineIndex": 80
    },
    {
      "start": 251.497,
      "end": 256.095,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that we went down to the land of our inheritance,",
      "verse": "3:22",
      "lineIndex": 82
    },
    {
      "start": 256.275,
      "end": 259.712,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and we did gather together our gold, and our silver,",
      "verse": "3:22",
      "lineIndex": 83
    },
    {
      "start": 259.892,
      "end": 261.517,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and our precious things.",
      "verse": "3:22",
      "lineIndex": 84
    },
    {
      "start": 262.197,
      "end": 264.844,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after we had gathered these things together,",
      "verse": "3:23",
      "lineIndex": 85
    },
    {
      "start": 265.024,
      "end": 267.903,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "we went up again unto the house of Laban.",
      "verse": "3:23",
      "lineIndex": 86
    },
    {
      "start": 268.583,
      "end": 272.902,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that we went in unto Laban, and desired him",
      "verse": "3:24",
      "lineIndex": 87
    },
    {
      "start": 273.082,
      "end": 275.358,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that he would give unto us the records",
      "verse": "3:24",
      "lineIndex": 88
    },
    {
      "start": 275.538,
      "end": 279.253,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which were engraven upon the plates of brass,",
      "verse": "3:24",
      "lineIndex": 89
    },
    {
      "start": 279.433,
      "end": 283.613,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for which we would give unto him our gold, and our silver,",
      "verse": "3:24",
      "lineIndex": 90
    },
    {
      "start": 283.793,
      "end": 285.651,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and all our precious things.",
      "verse": "3:24",
      "lineIndex": 91
    },
    {
      "start": 286.331,
      "end": 289.628,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that when Laban saw our property,",
      "verse": "3:25",
      "lineIndex": 92
    },
    {
      "start": 289.808,
      "end": 293.152,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and that it was exceedingly great, he did lust after it,",
      "verse": "3:25",
      "lineIndex": 93
    },
    {
      "start": 293.332,
      "end": 295.654,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "insomuch that he thrust us out,",
      "verse": "3:25",
      "lineIndex": 94
    },
    {
      "start": 295.834,
      "end": 298.017,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and sent his servants to slay us,",
      "verse": "3:25",
      "lineIndex": 95
    },
    {
      "start": 298.197,
      "end": 300.426,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that he might obtain our property.",
      "verse": "3:25",
      "lineIndex": 96
    },
    {
      "start": 301.106,
      "end": 305.1,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that we did flee before the servants of Laban,",
      "verse": "3:26",
      "lineIndex": 97
    },
    {
      "start": 305.28,
      "end": 308.577,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and we were obliged to leave behind our property,",
      "verse": "3:26",
      "lineIndex": 98
    },
    {
      "start": 308.757,
      "end": 311.125,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and it fell into the hands of Laban.",
      "verse": "3:26",
      "lineIndex": 99
    },
    {
      "start": 311.805,
      "end": 315.149,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that we fled into the wilderness,",
      "verse": "3:27",
      "lineIndex": 100
    },
    {
      "start": 315.329,
      "end": 318.487,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the servants of Laban did not overtake us,",
      "verse": "3:27",
      "lineIndex": 101
    },
    {
      "start": 318.667,
      "end": 321.407,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and we hid ourselves in the cavity of a rock.",
      "verse": "3:27",
      "lineIndex": 102
    },
    {
      "start": 322.087,
      "end": 325.152,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that Laman was angry with me,",
      "verse": "3:28",
      "lineIndex": 104
    },
    {
      "start": 325.332,
      "end": 327.05,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also with my father;",
      "verse": "3:28",
      "lineIndex": 105
    },
    {
      "start": 327.23,
      "end": 328.948,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also was Lemuel,",
      "verse": "3:28",
      "lineIndex": 106
    },
    {
      "start": 329.128,
      "end": 331.775,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for he hearkened unto the words of Laman.",
      "verse": "3:28",
      "lineIndex": 107
    },
    {
      "start": 331.955,
      "end": 336.506,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore Laman and Lemuel did speak many hard words unto us,",
      "verse": "3:28",
      "lineIndex": 108
    },
    {
      "start": 336.686,
      "end": 338.265,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "their younger brothers,",
      "verse": "3:28",
      "lineIndex": 109
    },
    {
      "start": 338.445,
      "end": 340.906,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they did smite us even with a rod.",
      "verse": "3:28",
      "lineIndex": 110
    },
    {
      "start": 341.586,
      "end": 344.651,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass as they smote us with a rod,",
      "verse": "3:29",
      "lineIndex": 111
    },
    {
      "start": 344.831,
      "end": 348.221,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "behold, an angel of the Lord came and stood before them,",
      "verse": "3:29",
      "lineIndex": 112
    },
    {
      "start": 348.401,
      "end": 350.166,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he spake unto them, saying:",
      "verse": "3:29",
      "lineIndex": 113
    },
    {
      "start": 350.346,
      "end": 353.365,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Why do ye smite your younger brother with a rod?",
      "verse": "3:29",
      "lineIndex": 114
    },
    {
      "start": 353.545,
      "end": 357.353,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Know ye not that the Lord hath chosen him to be a ruler over you,",
      "verse": "3:29",
      "lineIndex": 115
    },
    {
      "start": 357.533,
      "end": 359.855,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and this because of your iniquities?",
      "verse": "3:29",
      "lineIndex": 116
    },
    {
      "start": 360.035,
      "end": 362.589,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold ye shall go up to Jerusalem again,",
      "verse": "3:29",
      "lineIndex": 117
    },
    {
      "start": 362.769,
      "end": 365.555,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the Lord will deliver Laban into your hands.",
      "verse": "3:29",
      "lineIndex": 118
    },
    {
      "start": 366.235,
      "end": 369.161,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after the angel had spoken unto us, he departed.",
      "verse": "3:30",
      "lineIndex": 119
    },
    {
      "start": 369.841,
      "end": 372.07,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after the angel had departed,",
      "verse": "3:31",
      "lineIndex": 120
    },
    {
      "start": 372.25,
      "end": 375.408,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Laman and Lemuel again began to murmur, saying:",
      "verse": "3:31",
      "lineIndex": 121
    },
    {
      "start": 375.588,
      "end": 379.443,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "How is it possible that the Lord will deliver Laban into our hands?",
      "verse": "3:31",
      "lineIndex": 122
    },
    {
      "start": 379.623,
      "end": 382.967,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold, he is a mighty man, and he can command fifty,",
      "verse": "3:31",
      "lineIndex": 123
    },
    {
      "start": 383.147,
      "end": 386.305,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, even he can slay fifty; then why not us?",
      "verse": "3:31",
      "lineIndex": 124
    }
  ]
}